        public boolean enqueued()
        Determine if this item is contained in a queue.

      • increasePriority

        public void increasePriority()
        Increase the priority of this item in the queue. If this item is not contained in a queue, nothing happens.

        Determine the priority of this item relative to the given item.

        item - Priority queue item.
        Returns:
        True if this item has a higher priority than item, false otherwise.
